EXEC UpsertHelpDocumentation 'RegisterHelp', 'Help Registering User', '<h1><span style="color: rgb(204, 224, 245);">Password</span></h1><h4>The password requirement for SkaldBot is that your password must be a minimum of eight characters and have at least on letter and one number. Currently Skaldbot does not have a way to reset passwords so please do your best to keep track of your password.</h4><h1><br></h1><h1><span style="color: rgb(204, 224, 245);">Get Discord User ID</span></h1><h4>Make sure you have developer mode enabled</h4><ul><li>You''ll find Developer Mode in User Settings &gt; Appearance</li><li>To get the user id, right click your user name and select "Copy Id"</li></ul>', 1
EXEC UpsertHelpDocumentation 'AddServerHelp', 'Help Adding Server', '<h1><span style="color: rgb(204, 224, 245);">Get Discord Server ID</span></h1><h4>Make sure you have developer mode enabled</h4><ul><li>You''ll find Developer Mode in User Settings &gt; Appearance</li><li>To get the server id, right click your server and select "Copy Id"</li></ul>', 1